Change Log for update to WRF 3DVAR code
---------------------------------------

Author: Zhiquan Liu / John Bray
Reviewer: Dale Barker
Date: 02/14/06

Reason for changes (explain before making changes)
--------------------------------------------------

add radiance assimilation components

1. add RTTOV8_5 interface to WRF-VAR
2. add radiance innovation computations capability for NOAA and AUQA satellites
   contain NOAA HIRS/AMSUA/AMUSB and AUQA AIRS/AMSUA/HSB
3. add quality control for amsua/amsub
4. add bias correction interface (simple scan-dependent linear regression ).
5. modified namelist parameters

Test results (run on which machines?)
------------------------------------------------------

Tested 2 domains on bluesky :

WRF Hurricane (12km51L) domain - 00H 25 August 2005 data.
using cv_option=2 and GTS, NOAA-15/16 AMSU-A data

Tested same domain on ocotillo

